com.contentful.java.cda

Class ObserveQuery<T extends CDAResource>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.contentful.java.cda.ObserveQuery<T>

  • public final class ObserveQuery<T extends CDAResource>
extends Object
    Represents a query to the Delivery API which may be invoked via an Observable subscription. Observable requests are subscribed and observed on the same thread that executed the request. Call Observable.subscribeOn(Scheduler) and Observable.observeOn(Scheduler) to control that.
